CRM Analytics Settings

Create dataset from external files or via a URL from inside CRM Analytics.

Import from an external file

Locate a CSV, TSV, or XLSX data file, or a ZIP file containing multiple data files.
Tap either Open in... or the share icon ().
To begin importing data, tap the Analytics icon ().

Import via a URL from inside CRM Analytics

In the Playground, tap the settings icon () and tap Add Your Data. Then tap Add Data from a Remote Source and enter the URL for your data file. To paste a URL, touch and hold the text box. Then tap Import Data.

The CRM Analytics Data Connector guides you to create a dataset

With either approach, CRM Analytics launches the CRM Analytics Data Connector, which guides you through the rest of the data import process. Depending on your data file, the import process can include selecting the sheets to import from an XLSX file and mapping the data fields.

You’ll find your new dataset in a new CRM Analytics app in the navigation menu.
